snippet.textDisplay: Congratulations Philip Wang! I actually met you in 2001 or 2002 at Matthew Cheung’s house. You were a volleyball player back then and I was Matt’s younger family friend. I have been following your career from when you guys were doing voice overs and music videos like “seniorita and “simple things” to short stories like “stranger’s again”. The last 15-20 years you really became successful at your craft. I’m really happy for you and your future wife and future family.
